name: Blue
description: The community Solana token of InBetweeners. Doxxed founder and artists who have worked with @juventusfcen and @adidasfootball are now into meme coins. Founder is the same artist that designed Justin Biebers current PFP. The inBetweeners is a groundbreaking collection of 10,777 NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain, collaborating with the world's most iconic brands and individuals to revolutionize Web3 luxury fashion. At the heart of our project is Gianpiero, a world-renowned artist known for his work with Drew House, who brings each bear to life with his unique creative vision.
